obj_root_law:
  slug the-national-commission-for-indian-system-of-medicine-act-2020
  handle (15622)
  collectionHandle 123456789/1362
  title `The National Commission for Indian System of Medicine Act, 2020`
  actNumber (14)
  enactmentDate 2020-09-20
  sourceUrl `https://www.indiacode.nic.in/handle/123456789/15622`
  sources obj_root_law_sources
  sections obj_root_law_sections
  hindiTitle `राष्ट्रीय भारतीय चिकित्सा पद्धति आयोग अधिनियम, 2020`
  actYear (2020)
  ministry `Ministry of AYUSH`
  department undefined
  longTitle `An Act to provide for a medical education system that improves access to quality and affordable medical education, ensures availability of adequate and high quality medical professionals of Indian System of Medicine in all parts of the country that promotes equitable and universal healthcare that encourages community health perspective and makes services of such medical professionals accessible and affordable to all the citizens that promotes national health goals that encourages such medical professionals to adopt latest medical research in their work and to contribute to research that has an objective periodic and transparent assessment of medical institutions and facilitates maintenance of a medical register of Indian System of Medicine for India and enforces high ethical standards in all aspects of medical services that is flexible to adapt to the changing needs and has an effective grievance redressal mechanism and for matters connected therewith or incidental thereto.`
  enforcementDate `7th October, 2020 S. 3,4,5,6,8,11,18,19,20,21,54 and 55 vide notification No. S.O. 3483(E), dated 7th October, 2020, see Gazette of India, Extraordinary, Part II, sec. 3 (ii).`
  notification undefined
  fetchedAt `2026-05-09T18:27:20.434Z`
  translations obj_root_law_translations
